<h3>Payout Calculation:</h3>
<br>

<p>If you create a project and it does not receive enough donations to be completed, the creation fee is kept by the website. If a project receives excess donations, those donations are also kept by t\he website and not returned to you.</p>

<strong><p>Your total payout for the simulation is: <strong>(Credits not spent creating projects + Credits awarded for successful projects.)</strong>.</p></strong>     

<br>

<h3>Additional Instructions:</h3>
<br>      
<p> - You will play <strong><%= NUMBER_OF_PRACTICE_ROUNDS %></strong> practice rounds and <strong><%= NUMBER_OF_LIVE_ROUNDS %></strong> live rounds of this simulation. In each round, you will be randomly rematched with <strong><%= NUMBER_OF_DONORS_PER_GROUP %></strong> other donors and <strong><%= NUMBER_OF_CREATORS_PER_GROUP - 1 %></strong> other creator, so in every round you are playing with a different set of people. You will not know who else you are playing with.</p>    

<p> - In each round, the credits you earn will be added to a running total. At the end of the experiment, your credits will be exchanged for cash at a rate of (<strong><%= CREDITS_TO_DOLLAR_RATE %> credits for $1</strong>).</p>